@startuml
title ATM Control - Withdrawal Amount Selection

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForAmount
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state Dispensing
state Ejecting

Idle : entry / Display Welcome

Idle --> WaitingForAmount : Card Inserted / Get Amount


WaitingForAmount --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Predefined Amount Selected /\nRequest Withdrawal, Display Wait
WaitingForAmount --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Custom Amount Entered /\nRequest Withdrawal, Display Wait
WaitingForAmount --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

ProcessingWithdrawal --> Dispensing : Withdrawal Approved /\nDispense Cash, Update Status
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject

Dispensing --> Ejecting : Transaction Completed / Eject

Ejecting --> Idle : Card Ejected / Display Welcome
@enduml
